HEADWORD: Unprecedented
<hw>Un*prec"e*dent*ed</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having no
precedent or example; not preceded by a like case; not having the
authority of prior example; novel; new; unexampled.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Un*prec"e*dent*ed*ly</wf>,
<pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unpredict</ent>⟦br⟧
